title: Hclust - DMR4glm method
body: This is an implementation of Agnieszka Prochenka's Delete or Merge Regressors algorithm. Short overview: LTR statistics are calculated for models with merged exactly one pair of factor levels against the initial model. These statistics are used as distances in clustering that is run afterwards.
